      <text>Finding the Trigonometry Ratios in a 30°, 60° and 90° Triangle</text>
    </name>
    <questiontext format="moodle_auto_format">
      <text><![CDATA[Using the triangle below, find:
<p><ol type="a">
    <p>Find the length BC</p>
    <li> \( \sin 30^\circ \)</li>
    <li> \( \cos 60^\circ\)</li>
    <li>\( \tan 30^\circ \)</li>
</ol>
</p>
